Dalgety commercial director to retire . British agribusiness group Dalgety Plc said on Wednesday its commercial director Robert Harris would retire from the board on September 30 this year , when he will also relinquish his executive responsibilities . Harris joined Dalgety in April 1965 , became a director of Spillers Limited when it was bought by Dalgety in 1980 and joined the board as commercial director in 1987 . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 7717 
